data.description: Move in ready with many updates! Walk in to your living room and kitchen with cathedral ceilings and a dining area. Most of the main floor has been painted recently. The kitchen has a lot of counter space and wood cabinets. There is newer flooring in all bathrooms. The basement offers  egress windows, family room, rec room w/gas fireplace(remote operated), hobby room or possible 4th bedroom, 1/2 bath, and finished laundry room. New roof in 2021; A/C in 2022, newer insulated garage door, water heater, garbage disposal, recessed lighting in kitchen and primary bedroom. It has whirlpool appliances. Microwave and dishwasher are brand new! Garage has been finished and the deck off the kitchen has been reinforced for a hot tub w/ electrical box.
